    seoTitle: "Complete Beginner's Guide to SEO in 2024 | Marketing Hub",
    seoDescription: "Learn SEO from scratch. This beginner's guide covers how search engines work, the three pillars of SEO, and actionable first steps to start ranking higher today.",
