    content: `<h2>Quick Navigation</h2><p>Use the global search (press <code>/</code> or click the search icon at the top of the sidebar) to quickly jump to any section, website, keyword, or contact by name. The search works across all platform data — you can find a specific keyword, a lead by name, or a social post by content without navigating through menus.</p><h2>Saved Filters</h2><p>Most data tables in the platform (keywords, backlinks, leads) support custom filters. After applying filters you use regularly (e.g., keywords with position changes in the past 7 days, leads with "qualified" status), click "Save Filter" to name and save this filter configuration. Your saved filters appear in the filter dropdown for quick access in future sessions.</p><h2>Bulk Actions</h2><p>Select multiple items in any data table using the checkboxes to access bulk actions: bulk delete, bulk edit, bulk tag assignment, and bulk export. Bulk actions dramatically accelerate data management tasks that would take minutes to complete item by item. Use <code>Shift+click</code> to select a range of consecutive items or <code>Cmd/Ctrl+click</code> to select non-consecutive items individually.</p>`,
